{"tid":2086202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈：香 港 進 入 顏 色 革 命 時 代","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:01:02.000Z","uid":154486,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d18929b993022841e1340341d745d44601860e50","tid":2086202,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支共就係蘇聯<br />\n我地就係<br />\n第二次劇變既領頭人</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">我地既革命色就係黃黑</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS1iMaY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS1iMaY.jpg&h=74b422ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>顏色革命（Color revolution）</strong><br />\n又稱花朵革命，是指20世紀80、90年代開始的一系列發生在中亞、東歐獨聯體國家的以顏色命名，以「和平非暴力」方式進行的政權變更運動，而且這些運動有向包括中東的一些地區在內的地方蔓延的趨勢。參與者們以支持自由民主與普世價值為目標，通常是現有政權的反對者。他們通常採用一種特別的顏色或者花朵來作為他們的標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r82qreP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr82qreP.jpg&h=7515ba52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLZoXmv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLZoXmv.jpg&h=d5f0f468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0MKGN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0MKGN9.jpg&h=eb7b05ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVtw6eO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVtw6eO.jpg&h=7a1c565c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GLbR6eM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGLbR6eM.jpg&h=73c7b663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XPTz75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XPTz75.jpg&h=de85c124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjUgxUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjUgxUK.jpg&h=1b0875f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQNmJ1o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQNmJ1o.jpg&h=3e905817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2CRmN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2CRmN3.jpg&h=18a02a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pe4GON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pe4GON.jpg&h=342820a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大家係時候要承認<br />\n呢一場唔再係要求改革既<br />\n社會運動<br />\n<br />\n呢一場<br />\n係以推翻港偽政權<br />\n自強獨立為目標既<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">顏色革命</span></ins></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"5658a292d4985e598e358398209d4385141b5705","tid":2086202,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"洋紫荊革命"},{"pid":"ec7cadb6e0926a148b9d713bb1ebd028273d3f90","tid":2086202,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"黃黑色就係我地既革命色"},{"pid":"53471f8a6711736c37f5991a64f3816ac81e0042","tid":2086202,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67cec8400b24374122a6713b3cc629220c5d1f2","tid":2086202,"uid":68111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jzPSY1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jzPSY1.gif&h=4d6f011e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b51acaacdfaac0a92089603d18ff9d41a6e6cc28","tid":2086202,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"s